=Discussion=

==The Four Pillars==

"1. Decentralized communications:

2 essential components:

-	The internet & p2p decentralized technology

-	Cryptography (to avoid surveillance & censorship by centralized authorities)


2. Decentralized Law

(First communicate what we want to do, then come to agreement on how to cooperate, therefore need of decentralized law)

3 essential components:

-	Choice of law

-	Choice of judicator

-	Choice of enforcer


3. Decentralized Production

2 essential components:

-	Decentralized materials production (3D printing)

-	Decentralized energy production

(Small scale production at home without censorship)


4. Decentralized Finance

2 essential components:

-	Decentralized currency (Bitcoin)

-	Decentralized contracting systems (offer complete universal transaction platform) "



